Jason Cerbone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_Cerbone 0 Jason Cerbone (born November 2, 1977 in Yonkers, New York) is an American actor. He is most notable for the role of Jackie Aprile, Jr. on the hit HBO series The Sopranos. Jason_Cerbone ( born November_2_,_1977 in Yonkers , New_York ) is an_American_actor .
